#impact-page
  %header.mb-64.flex.flex-col.items-center
    .md-container
    %h1.text-h5.text-textColor6.mb-16.flex.items-center
      = graphical_icon "report", css_class: 'h-[26px] w-[26px] filter-textColor6 mr-16'
      Exercism Impact Report
    %h2.text-h0.mb-12.text-center{ class: 'max-w-[800px]' }
      We‚Äôve provided
      %strong{ class: 'pl-8 pr-12 font-bold bg-[url(graphics/impact-highlight.svg)] bg-[length:100%_100%]' } 82,045,205
      minutes of free education.
    %p.font-medium.text-textColor6.text-24.leading-160.text-center{ class: 'max-w-[780px]' }
      And increasing ‚Äî by 600,000 minutes per day!‚Ä®
      %br
      All on a free, open source project funded by people like you.

  .md-container.mb-48
    .flex.items-stretch
      .mr-32{ class: 'w-fill max-w-[380px]' }
        .shadow-lgZ1.py-8.rounded-16.mb-32
          .py-12.px-32
            %h3.label-large Students
            .text-purple.font-semibold.text-40.leading-150
              = render ReactComponents::Impact::Stat.new(:sign_up_metric, 1_008_385)
            .text-successColor.font-bold +939 per day

          .py-12.px-32.bg-bgGray
            %h3.label-large Exercises Practiced
            .text-purple.font-semibold.text-40.leading-150
              = render ReactComponents::Impact::Stat.new(:start_solution_metric, 3_800_957)
            .text-successColor.font-bold +1,842 per day

          .py-12.px-32
            %h3.label-large Mentoring Discussions
            .text-purple.font-semibold.text-40.leading-150 268,000

        .bg-bgGray.shadow-base.py-16.px-24
          %h3.text-h5.mb-4 Exercism teaches #{Track.active.count} programming languages, from #{Track.active.order('title ASC').first.title} to #{Track.active.order('title ASC').last.title}.
          %p.text-p-large Using a unique blend of learning, practicing, and mentoring. Everything on Exercism is 100% free.

      .shadow-lg.flex-grow.bg-white.rounded-16.p-24
        = ReactComponents::Impact::Map.new([])

  .md-container.mb-64
    .grid.grid-cols-3.gap-20
      - 3.times do
        .flex.flex-col.py-20.px-24
          .flex.items-center.mb-12
            = image_tag "photos/twitter-zippkode.jpg", class: 'w-[40px] h-[40px] rounded-circle mr-12'
            .flex.flex-col
              .label-large Karl üá∫üá¶
              .text-p-base.text-textColor6 @zippcode
            = link_to icon('external-site-twitter', 'Twitter', css_class: 'filter-twitter h-[16px] w-[16px]'), "https://twitter.com/zippkode/status/1561075536834838530", class: 'ml-auto p-8'
          %p.text-p-large
            ‚Äú...I worked on the Ruby strings exercises at
            %em.not-italic.font-medium.text-purple @exercism_io
            This platform forces me to slow down and actually logically solve the tasks...‚Äù

  .md-container.mb-64
    .flex
      .mr-32.shadow-lg.flex-grow.bg-white.rounded-16.py-40.px-48
        %h2.text-h1.mb-32 Exercism is powered by huge team of wonderful volunteers.
        .grid.grid-cols-3.gap-20
          .flex.flex-col
            .text-40.leading-150.font-semibold.text-purple 11,375
            .label-large Mentors
          .flex.flex-col
            .text-40.leading-150.font-semibold.text-purple 4,696
            .label-large Code Contributors
          .flex.flex-col
            .text-40.leading-150.font-semibold.text-purple 6
            .label-large Full-time Staff

      %div{ class: 'w-fill max-w-[374px]' }
        .p-24.shadow-base.mb-32.bg-bgGray
          %h3.text-h4.mb-8 Has Exercism helped you become a better developer?
          %p.text-p-large.mb-16 If Exercism has helped your career prospects or given you joy, please consider financially supporting us.
          %p.text-p-large Only 1% of people that use Exercism support us. Please be one of them.

        .btn.btn-base.btn-secondary
          See how you can support us
          = graphical_icon "arrow-right"

  .md-container.mb-64
    %h3.text-h3.text-center.mb-16 A special thanks to these organisations...
    .logos.flex.items-center.justify-center.flex-wrap.gap-64.mb-24
      = icon "mozilla", "Mozilla", category: :partners, css_class: "mozilla"
      = icon "gobridge", "GoBridge", category: :partners, css_class: "gobridge"
      = icon "chicago", "University of Chicago", category: :partners, css_class: "chicago"
      = icon "thalamus", "Thalamus AI", category: :partners
    .text-center.text-18.leading-150.text-textColor6.font-semibold
      And over
      %a.underline{ href: '#', title: 'Individual donors' } 700 individuals donors!

  = ReactComponents::Impact::Chart.new([])
